66
00:02:38,471 --> 00:02:40,605
<i>if you lived</i>
<i>with that kind of humidity.</i>

67
00:02:40,638 --> 00:02:43,605
<i>The existence of this being</i>
<i>caused a warp in space,</i>

68
00:02:43,638 --> 00:02:46,105
