FIGHT THEM ALL OVER AGAIN?

197
00:08:10,377 --> 00:08:13,277
THIS IS THE WORST NIGHTMARE
I'VE EVER BEEN AWAKE FOR!

198
00:08:13,311 --> 00:08:15,744
