TOO MUCH TO GIVE UP NOW.

203
00:08:26,177 --> 00:08:29,611
YOU FOOLS! YOU HAVEN'T
EVEN SEEN MY TRUE POWER YET.

204
00:08:29,644 --> 00:08:32,044
