HOW IT FEELS

211
00:08:42,811 --> 00:08:45,511
TO BE ONE STEP CLOSER
TO EXTINCTION.

212
00:08:52,944 --> 00:08:54,144
[ GASPS ]

213
00:08:54,177 --> 00:08:55,944
