SO EASILY!

215
00:08:58,144 --> 00:08:59,211
I'M SORRY, T.K.

216
00:08:59,244 --> 00:09:01,411
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.
IT'S HIS.

217
00:09:01,444 --> 00:09:03,544
GREAT. THIS TIME
WE'RE FINISHED.

218
00:09:03,577 --> 00:09:05,811
YOU BETTER LOSE
THAT 'TUDE, KARI.

219
00:09:05,844 --> 00:09:08,344
JUST BECAUSE WE'RE AT
THE ROOKIE LEVEL

220
00:09:08,377 --> 00:09:10,777
DOESN'T MEAN
WE STILL CAN'T FIGHT.

221
00:09:10,811 --> 00:09:13,744
THAT'S IT! START FROM SCRATCH.
YOU CAN DIGEVOLVE AGAIN.

222
00:09:13,777 --> 00:09:15,744
WE'D HAVE TO EAT SOMETHING.

223
00:09:15,777 --> 00:09:16,744
I <i>AM</i> HUNGRY.

224
00:09:16,777 --> 00:09:19,211
FORGET FOOD. WE HAVE
THE POWER WITHIN US.

225
00:09:19,244 --> 00:09:22,477
BUT WE NEED YOUR HELP.

